00:08:49.970 --> 00:08:51.030
But it wasn't loud.

00:08:51.200 --> 00:08:52.800
Did Eryong's family hear it?

00:08:52.960 --> 00:08:55.160
Eryong's family didn't hear anything.

00:08:55.600 --> 00:08:57.060
That couple sleeps early.

00:08:57.200 --> 00:08:59.240
They said they didn't hear anything.

00:08:59.240 --> 00:08:59.840
But there were also

00:08:59.840 --> 00:09:00.790
several households
that didn't hear either.

00:09:00.790 --> 00:09:01.650
That's normal.

00:09:01.870 --> 00:09:03.150
Eryong's wife said

00:09:03.600 --> 00:09:06.550
she fell asleep
while listening to the weather forecast.

00:09:06.550 --> 00:09:07.840
Didn't she watch "An Addiction to Love"?

00:09:07.840 --> 00:09:08.480
Eryong said

00:09:08.480 --> 00:09:09.880
he watched it for a while,

00:09:10.120 --> 00:09:10.910
then the couple

00:09:10.910 --> 00:09:12.480
went to bed one after another,

00:09:12.480 --> 00:09:14.000
about half an hour apart.

00:09:14.870 --> 00:09:15.670
This is the statement of

00:09:15.670 --> 00:09:17.330
Eryong's neighbor opposite.

00:09:17.840 --> 00:09:18.600
They said in the middle of the night,

00:09:18.600 --> 00:09:20.800
they heard Eryong throwing something.

00:09:20.840 --> 00:09:22.120
Couldn't tell if it's throwing things

00:09:22.120 --> 00:09:22.720
or emptying chamber pot.

00:09:22.720 --> 00:09:23.960
They couldn't see clearly.

00:09:23.960 --> 00:09:25.120
By that time, the TV series

00:09:25.120 --> 00:09:26.380
had already finished.

00:09:29.240 --> 00:09:30.220
The neighbor said

00:09:30.220 --> 00:09:30.360
[Question: Please describe in detail
how loud the sound was.]

00:09:30.360 --> 00:09:31.810
the volume of Eryong's TV

00:09:31.810 --> 00:09:32.110
[Ugh, it was like having a loudspeaker
right next to your ear!]

00:09:32.110 --> 00:09:33.110
was turned way up.

00:09:33.480 --> 00:09:33.810
They could even hear
"Confused Love" playing.

00:09:33.810 --> 00:09:35.790
[I could feel the wall vibrating
right through the bed.]

00:09:35.790 --> 00:09:36.850
What time was that?

00:09:38.720 --> 00:09:40.360
You took notes in great detail,

00:09:40.360 --> 00:09:42.620
but still didn't notice anything wrong.

00:09:58.080 --> 00:09:58.670
Ran.

00:09:59.750 --> 00:09:59.810
Want a haircut?

00:09:59.810 --> 00:10:00.720
[Eryong Barbershop]

00:10:00.720 --> 00:10:01.720
Let me get a shave.

00:10:01.910 --> 00:10:02.320
Sure.

00:10:02.790 --> 00:10:03.250
Come on.

00:10:05.840 --> 00:10:06.390
Okay.

00:10:18.120 --> 00:10:18.870
Eryong?

00:10:20.000 --> 00:10:20.750
Eryong?

00:10:21.800 --> 00:10:24.750
[Eryong Barbershop]

00:10:24.750 --> 00:10:25.270
Hello.

00:10:26.320 --> 00:10:27.320
Is my mentor here?

00:10:27.790 --> 00:10:28.520
He's inside.

00:10:31.790 --> 00:10:33.750
Can't you hear now?

00:10:35.360 --> 00:10:36.600
It was quite late that night

00:10:36.600 --> 00:10:37.440
when you were here.

00:10:37.440 --> 00:10:38.840
Everything was so quiet.

00:10:39.080 --> 00:10:40.270
That girl who was attacked

00:10:40.270 --> 00:10:41.870
didn't make any noise at all?

00:10:42.440 --> 00:10:43.900
You didn't hear anything?

00:10:44.150 --> 00:10:44.840
No, Ran.

00:10:44.840 --> 00:10:45.670
I really didn't hear anything.

00:10:45.670 --> 00:10:46.440
I was asleep.

00:10:47.550 --> 00:10:48.480
Falling asleep?

00:10:48.720 --> 00:10:50.250
Really slept that heavily?

00:10:51.360 --> 00:10:52.840
Well, that's not fair.

00:10:53.200 --> 00:10:54.080
I did come out

00:10:54.080 --> 00:10:55.410
to empty my chamber pot.

00:10:55.630 --> 00:10:56.360
After I went back,

00:10:56.360 --> 00:10:58.150
I fell asleep as soon as
my head hit the pillow.

00:10:58.150 --> 00:10:58.550
It's true.

00:10:58.550 --> 00:11:00.030
My wife didn't hear anything either.

00:11:00.030 --> 00:11:00.720
We couldn't help.

00:11:00.720 --> 00:11:01.720
I'm really sorry.

00:11:03.480 --> 00:11:04.080
By the way,

00:11:04.550 --> 00:11:05.030
Ran,

00:11:05.360 --> 00:11:06.550
did you catch the guy?

00:11:06.550 --> 00:11:07.320
Who did it?

00:11:09.390 --> 00:11:11.000
I can't tell you that.

00:11:14.120 --> 00:11:15.320
Why don't you turn off

00:11:15.360 --> 00:11:16.490
your TV set at night?

00:11:17.720 --> 00:11:18.320
My TV set?

00:11:20.120 --> 00:11:21.380
I turn it off every day.

00:11:23.320 --> 00:11:24.050
The thing is,

00:11:25.480 --> 00:11:27.010
you had the volume too loud.

00:11:27.240 --> 00:11:28.080
I've been planning

00:11:28.080 --> 00:11:30.080
to talk to you about this several times.

00:11:30.080 --> 00:11:30.880
It's fine now.

00:11:31.200 --> 00:11:32.400
I already handled it.

00:11:33.360 --> 00:11:34.390
I've talked to

00:11:34.510 --> 00:11:35.910
your neighbors about it.

00:11:39.150 --> 00:11:39.670
Well,

00:11:39.870 --> 00:11:40.960
thank you, Ran.

00:11:40.960 --> 00:11:41.910
Forgetting to turn off the TV

00:11:41.910 --> 00:11:43.370
caused such a big problem.

00:11:46.200 --> 00:11:47.360
You and your wife

00:11:47.510 --> 00:11:48.710
both sleep very well.

00:11:49.960 --> 00:11:51.690
It's easy for us to fall asleep.

00:11:53.080 --> 00:11:54.010
What a blessing.

00:11:56.080 --> 00:11:57.760
That's because of my job.

00:11:58.000 --> 00:11:58.720
Every day,

00:11:58.740 --> 00:12:00.510
I have to work on customers' faces

00:12:00.510 --> 00:12:01.480
and heads.

00:12:01.480 --> 00:12:02.390
If I don't sleep well,

00:12:02.390 --> 00:12:03.600
I wouldn't dare do this job.

00:12:03.600 --> 00:12:04.660
My wife is the same.

00:12:08.720 --> 00:12:09.980
You have no questions?

00:12:11.840 --> 00:12:13.320
Weren't you always wanting
to

00:12:13.320 --> 00:12:14.380
ask him something?

00:12:15.000 --> 00:12:15.930
I just want to ask

00:12:16.120 --> 00:12:17.980
if you and your wife sleep so well,

00:12:18.030 --> 00:12:19.910
why do you take so many sleeping pills?

00:12:19.910 --> 00:12:21.270
Three bottles in six months.

00:12:21.270 --> 00:12:22.080
One pill a day?

00:12:23.790 --> 00:12:24.550
Funny thing.

00:12:25.120 --> 00:12:26.390
I heard that
before Huang Hui committed suicide,

00:12:26.390 --> 00:12:28.050
she also took sleeping pills.

00:12:28.270 --> 00:12:29.930
No idea where she bought them.

00:12:30.360 --> 00:12:32.000
It's really strange.

00:12:35.550 --> 00:12:36.880
"An Addiction to Love",

00:12:37.390 --> 00:12:39.590
do you remember which episode it was on?

00:12:40.770 --> 00:12:42.000
Do you know what the original title novel

00:12:42.000 --> 00:12:43.800
"Addiction to Love" was called?

00:12:44.120 --> 00:12:44.720
Zhao,

00:12:45.270 --> 00:12:46.630
tell your Brother Eryong

00:12:46.630 --> 00:12:47.630
what it is called.

00:12:47.840 --> 00:12:49.640
"One Last Thrill Before Death".

00:12:52.870 --> 00:12:53.750
That's right.

00:12:54.720 --> 00:12:56.850
There's one last thrill before death.

00:12:57.030 --> 00:12:57.960
Ran, I was wrong.

00:13:00.360 --> 00:13:01.270
I'm not a decent man!

00:13:01.270 --> 00:13:02.720
I was wrong, Ran.

00:13:06.910 --> 00:13:08.550
What are you standing there for?

00:13:08.550 --> 00:13:10.680
Hurry with the interrogation record!

00:13:11.440 --> 00:13:12.050
Get up.

00:13:12.150 --> 00:13:13.210
Tell us in details.

00:13:17.910 --> 00:13:18.840
Feeling better?

00:13:20.910 --> 00:13:22.030
Let's have a chat.

00:13:24.240 --> 00:13:24.870
Go ahead.

00:13:27.790 --> 00:13:29.910
We just came back from Eryong's place.

00:13:29.910 --> 00:13:30.640
To be honest,

00:13:33.000 --> 00:13:34.200
I've been wondering,

00:13:34.870 --> 00:13:36.870
why would Liu Ke come to my precinct?

00:13:37.440 --> 00:13:39.370
She doesn't even live around here.

00:13:43.840 --> 00:13:45.320
Because her mom is a slut.

00:13:46.910 --> 00:13:49.570
Her mom didn't want to
stay with her dad anymore.

00:13:50.030 --> 00:13:52.960
So she had an affair with
one of her former classmate.

00:13:55.200 --> 00:13:56.080
Did Liu Ke know?

00:13:58.600 --> 00:13:59.390
I don't know.

00:14:02.910 --> 00:14:03.710
I have no idea.

00:14:10.600 --> 00:14:12.200
I went out a bit late that day.

00:14:19.480 --> 00:14:21.150
I think she saw me.

00:14:22.960 --> 00:14:24.760
I couldn't let her see me, right?

00:14:26.360 --> 00:14:27.240
I had to hide.

00:15:02.720 --> 00:15:03.440
Hello?

00:15:04.840 --> 00:15:05.570
Anyone here?

00:15:33.440 --> 00:15:34.120
If she couldn't find me,

00:15:34.120 --> 00:15:35.580
she'd just go back, right?

00:15:37.080 --> 00:15:39.150
Why wasn't the child at school?

00:15:41.630 --> 00:15:42.890
Actually, that day...

00:15:42.910 --> 00:15:43.840
Write this down.

00:15:45.200 --> 00:15:46.510
Question everything first!

00:15:46.510 --> 00:15:47.710
Don't interrupt her.

