I forgot to run virus scan.

00:41:49.800 --> 00:41:51.280
My hard drive doesn't need it.

00:41:51.280 --> 00:41:52.230
Even police can't guarantee

00:41:52.230 --> 00:41:53.320
there are no viruses.

00:41:53.320 --> 00:41:54.190
You've already copied everything.

00:41:54.190 --> 00:41:55.550
what's the point of virus scanning now?

00:41:55.550 --> 00:41:56.800
It'll be done soon.

00:42:00.550 --> 00:42:01.440
Scan what?

00:42:02.110 --> 00:42:03.640
Mentor, virus scanning...

00:42:17.840 --> 00:42:20.000
So we just need to stare at this Shih Tzu

00:42:20.710 --> 00:42:22.110
bouncing around here...

00:42:23.510 --> 00:42:24.770
And then the little dog

00:42:25.480 --> 00:42:26.230
will be killed?